(original English text if my translation above is not understandable)
I have videos that might be of help for Aquatic Mine 2nd and 5th missions, but I am not sure.  The method has only been tested on DC, but not GC.
http://youtube.com/watch?v=flgpzwEkOWI
http://youtube.com/watch?v=rhv5heDTJgU
The walls can be grabbed from underwater by pressing A+B.
The 5th mission video does not get enough points for rank A, but if the order is reversed and the method works, the score will be 15360 with rank A, because GC will have 1 extra ring and 6 extra mine carts to add to the 5230 score in the video.</TEXTAREA></TD>

